Hardware required:
  2x L298n dual H bridge 
  4x DC Motors
  Pasberry Pi 3b
  Power Source packs for dedicated 5V to each pieve of hardware (pi and each controller). Can be combined in parallel 
  
  
  Schematic configuration:
    1st contoller
      IN1, IN2, IN3, IN4 connected to rasberry pi GPIO pins 
    2nd controller
      IN1, IN2, IN3, IN4 connected to rasberry pi GPIO pins 
    Each controller 5V hot to battery pack and ground to ground on rasberry pi
    
   Motor set up is for 2 motors per controller connected into the same OUT1 and OUT2
